title: Cowboys-Eagles, Bears, Lamar Jackson, and where Colin was right & wrong
itunes:title: Cowboys-Eagles, Bears, Lamar Jackson, and where Colin was right & wrong
description:
Colin discusses the Dallas Cowboys and why they are now dangerous, the problems with the Philadelphia Eagles, what the Chicago Bears need do to get over the hump, why he enjoys watching Baltimore Ravens QB Lamar Jackson, and where he was right and wrong over the weekend. Guests include Travis Kelce, Michael Vick, Matt Mosley, and Trent Dilfer.
